4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Participants gain essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The course emphasizes risk management, data loss prevention strategies, and navigating compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop